LanguageData.MaxStackLimitStat.Text:
Represents the stack limit for {0} on this shelf. The maximum value is calculated from
1. Normal StackLimit = {1}
2. Max Overstack Ratio = x{2}
3. Overstack Limit = {1} x{2} = {3}
4. MaxMassPerRackedThing = MaxStockWeight / RackLimit = {4}
5. MassStackLimit = MaxMassPerRackedThing / NormalThingMass = {5}
6. MaxStackLimit = Minimum(OverstackLimit, MassLimit) = {6}
